Installing in Ubuntu Linux
--------------------------

- Download and install the following Google Flags libraries from:

	https://code.google.com/p/gflags/downloads/list

	libgflags0_2.0-1_i386.deb
	libgflags-dev_2.0-1_i386.deb

- Download, compile and install Google Log libraries from:

	http://code.google.com/p/google-glog/downloads/detail?name=glog-0.3.2.tar.gz&can=2&q=

	cd Libs/glog-0.3.2/
	./configure
	make
	sudo make install

- Download the Google Ceres library from:
	
	http://code.google.com/p/ceres-solver/

- Configure and generate the Ceres project for Code::Blocks (or your preferred IDE)

- Compile the Google Ceres library.
